narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: Many of the finer points of ethical behavior/best practices for software development were new to me. I knew quite a bit about intellectual honesty in the context of the humanities, but it was helpful for me to consider cases in which collaboration and shared datasets were involved.
